            </p>
        </dd>
    </dl>
</li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-6 views-row-even">
    <a href="/ko/node/419" class="thumb"><span><img src="https://kyeol.kr/sites/default/files/styles/article_thumbnail/public/field/image/%ED%97%A4%EB%8D%94%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80_%EC%A3%BC%EC%A0%84%EC%9E%A5_%EC%8A%A4%ED%8B%B8.jpg?itok=BK2yK_xc" alt="‘주전장’을 줌인하다 - 영화 &lt;주전장&gt; 미키 데자키 감독 인터뷰 "/></span></a>
